Tape and photos were released of a US boy with his teacher, Debra LaFave, accused of seducing him.
LaFave, a former schoolteacher, was recorded arranging encounters with the 14-year-old student.
She pleaded guilty to lewd acts and avoided prison.
The boy revealed details of their relationship, including LaFave's troubled marriage.
Despite plea negotiations breaking down, LaFave received three years of house arrest and probation.
The case attracted national attention, with media coverage from around the world.
LaFave, now a registered sex offender, faces challenges ahead due to her actions and mental health issues.
